WEBVTT

00:00.917 --> 00:02.111
Iron man: Las Vegas.

00:02.158 --> 00:04.239
Everyone on your best behavior.

00:04.286 --> 00:05.404
Nice view, iron man,

00:05.451 --> 00:07.563
but I'm guessing
that's not why we're here.

00:07.610 --> 00:08.924
This is where
the security alert said

00:08.971 --> 00:10.595
Maximus would be, Hawkeye.

00:11.762 --> 00:13.035
Black widow: Maximus?

00:13.082 --> 00:15.151
Hulk: Black bolt's
brother, tech genius.

00:15.198 --> 00:16.627
Got a thing against humans.

00:16.674 --> 00:18.929
Heard the inhumans exiled him.

00:18.976 --> 00:20.156
What's he planning?

00:20.203 --> 00:21.172
Don't know, cap.

00:21.219 --> 00:23.148
Black bolt didn't
include any details.

00:23.203 --> 00:24.773
I assume the alert
came from him.

00:24.828 --> 00:28.134
It's one dude.
How hard is this gonna be?

00:36.210 --> 00:38.577
I should know by now not to ask.

00:41.182 --> 00:44.516
(People screaming)

00:47.722 --> 00:50.252
Iron man: Where did Maximus
find such pathetic goons?

00:50.518 --> 00:51.839
Falcon:
Off to the side, please.

00:51.899 --> 00:54.366
Thor: You'll be more
comfortable over there.

00:55.329 --> 00:57.829
Goons are covered.
Take the fight to Maximus.

00:59.000 --> 01:05.074
